{
  "texts": [
    "We would expect even less content misclassification for this dataset if meaningless text were also removed.",
    "While these results are not perfect, they represent a significant improvement upon the non-punctuated analyses.",
    "Results: Picture description task (Strikwerda-Brown et al., 2021)",
    "Our model correctly identified much of the internal content (Fig. 8a; r =.87, p < 0.001) and external content (Fig.",
    "8b, r =.64, p < 0.001) in picture descriptions."
  ]
}